# Keeps the Docker build context small and cache-friendly. Build context is
# the repository root (see infrastructure/docker/frontend.Dockerfile) — every
# app's Dockerfile COPYs only the paths it needs explicitly, so nothing here
# is required for the build itself, only excluded to speed up `docker build`
# and avoid invalidating layer cache on unrelated file changes.

.git
.github
.claude
.ai
.angular
.nx
.vscode
.idea

node_modules
dist
tmp
out-tsc
coverage

*.log
build-output.txt
build.log
frontend.log

.env
.env.*
!.env.example

infrastructure/kubernetes
infrastructure/terraform
infrastructure/docs
infrastructure/monitoring

README.md
patheya-express-frontend
